          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "College Have NCC In that Army Wing and Naval wing",
          "name": "Vivek Gupta",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The auditorium is very good in condition as it has latest technologies.",
          "name": "shubham shingade",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "In each classrooms there are wifi connection and projectors which is also the best thing about this college.",
          "name": "shubham shingade",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Im an english student and the english lab, infrastructure, buildings, equipments all are really really good and money well spent by the college. The library is also one of the biggest library in all of india with over 1,00,000 books present.",
